  "description": "CO₂ laser (10.6μm, 100W-20kW) or fiber laser (1.06μm, 100W-30kW) focused beam welding. Keyhole mode: deep narrow welds (depth-to-width 5:1 to 15:1), speed 1-20 m/min. Conduction mode: shallow welds for thin materials. Fiber laser deliverable through flexible fiber optic — easily robot-integrated. High-speed precision welding for semiconductor equipment components.",
